Interface IDocumentTermList

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DocumentTermList

    public interface IDocumentTermList
    Defines the methods a documentTerm list needs to implement for a dictionary. Specifically, this list stores hashed terms as keys and term frequency as values.
